sources.title: Concrete Cowboys
sources.description: Tom Selleck and Jerry Reed are a couple of con-artist cowboys from Montana who end up in Nashville in the adventure of their lives.

sources.title: Concrete Cowboys (1979) TOM SELLECK
sources.description:
Stars: Tom Selleck, Jerry Reed, Morgan Fairchild 
Directed by: Burt Kennedy

A pair of Montana saddle tramps head for Nashville to open up a detective agency, but soon learn they are better at handling cows when they become entwined in an intricate blackmail scheme.

metadata.Plot: Two ex-cowboys from Montana wind up on the run when they are set up by a corrupt sheriff. They arrive in Nashville, where they open up a detective agency and soon they are hired to foil a kidnapping involving a singer.
metadata.Actors: Jerry Reed, Tom Selleck, Morgan Fairchild
